@page "/faq"
@inject HttpClient Http

<PageTitle>FAQ</PageTitle>

<div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">

    <h1 style="font-size: 2.2rem; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Frequently Asked Questions
    </h1>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>Can we rent racquets?</strong><br />
        Yes, for a nominal fee.
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>Are balls sold?</strong><br />
        Yes, available for purchase at cost.
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>Can we bring in our own food/beverages?</strong><br />
        With prior coordination, food can be brought in — but no outside alcohol is allowed. Adult beverages are available for purchase at TSP.
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>Restroom on premises?</strong><br />
        Yes, exclusively for TSP patrons.
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>Number of courts?</strong><br />
        One.
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>Night lighting?</strong><br />
        Yes.
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>Are pets allowed?</strong><br />
        No.
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>Is there a sitting area?</strong><br />
        Yes — includes a table, chairs, and a picnic table.
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>Is music allowed?</strong><br />
        Yes! A party speaker is provided and can be synced via Bluetooth.
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>What’s the cancellation policy?</strong><br />
        Cancel at least two hours before your scheduled time to avoid a fee. Late cancellations may incur a $20 charge.
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>Can we feed the goats?</strong><br />
        No — Starsky and Hutch have plenty to eat in the woods. They enjoy watching pickleball!
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <strong>Hours of operation?</strong><br />
        7:00 AM – 9:00 PM daily, unless otherwise posted on the website.
    </div>

</div>
